  "prompt": "What's Home Depot's return/exchange policy?",
  "response": "Home Depot\u2019s return/exchange policy is customer-friendly and designed to ensure satisfaction. Here are the key points:\n\n### **General Return Policy**\n- **Timeframe**: Most new, unopened merchandise can be returned within 90 days of purchase for a full refund or exchange.\n- **Receipt Requirement**: Receipts or proof of purchase (e.g., credit card statement or order confirmation) are required for returns or exchanges.\n- **Condition**: Items must be in their original packaging and in resalable condition.\n\n### **Special Exceptions**\n- **Major Appliances**: Returns or exchanges for major appliances (e.g., refrigerators, washers, dryers) must be made within 48 hours of delivery if in an unopened or unused condition.\n- **Special Order Items**: Custom or special order items may not be returnable unless defective or damaged.\n- **Hazardous Materials**: Items like pesticides, paint, and chemicals are generally not returnable unless defective.\n- **Seasonal Items**: Seasonal items (e.g., holiday decorations) must be returned within 30 days of purchase.\n\n### **Exchanges**\n- Defective or damaged items may be exchanged for the same item or a comparable product.\n\n### **Online Purchases**\n- Items purchased online can be returned to a Home Depot store or by mail using the return shipping label provided.\n\n### **Store Credit**\n- If you don\u2019t have a receipt, Home Depot may offer store credit based on the item\u2019s current selling price.\n\n### **Extended Return Policy**\n- Home Depot occasionally offers extended return periods, such as during the holiday season (e.g., purchases made between November 1 and December 31 may be returnable until January 31).\n\n### **Pro Desk Customers**\n- Contractors and Pro Desk customers may have different return policies based on their account agreements.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, check [Home Depot\u2019s official return policy page](https://www.homedepot.com/c/returns) or contact your local store.",
